<center><table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>
<center><strong>Spirit of Wolf</strong></center>
</font></td></tr>
</table></center>
<table width=70%>
<tr><td>Mana:</td>
<td>40</td></tr>
<tr><td>Skill:</td>
<td>Alteration</td></tr>
<tr><td valign=top>
Classes:</td>
<td>
<a href="/spells/druid.shtml">
Druid</a>
 (14)<BR>
<a href="/spells/ranger.shtml">
Ranger</a>
 (39)<BR>
<a href="/spells/shaman.shtml">
Shaman</a>
 (9)<BR>
</td></tr>
<tr><td>Buyable:</td><td>
Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>Researchable:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Drops from MOB:</td><td>
No</td></tr>
<tr><td>Cast Time:</td>
<td>4.50 seconds</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2><br></td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>Description:</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
Increases the target's movement rate by up to 55%.<BR>
<BR>
Duration of 360 ticks.  Can only be cast outdoors.</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan=2>
<BR>1 tick = 6 seconds<BR>
When a range of effects are given, it usually means that the effect becomes more potent as the caster increases in levels.
</td></tr>
